decks.notes: This Jund aggro deck relies on sacrificing creatures for value, utilizing cards like Witch's Oven and Mayhem Devil to control the board and deal damage to the opponent. Korvold, Fae-Cursed King acts as a powerful threat that can draw cards and grow in size with each sacrifice. The deck aims to pressure the opponent with quick and efficient creatures while generating card advantage through sacrifice synergies. The inclusion of Village Rites and Deadly Dispute allows the deck to maintain card advantage and pressure opponents with its aggressive playstyle.
